description: Only using ingredients of the utmost quality, including naturally raised, locally grown, organic and non-GMO meats, this hot pink truck’s menu features an eclectic selection of the best sandwiches and burgers from coast to coast. They’re bringing the vibrant flavors of the bayou straight to you with their Louisiana Po-Boy- shrimp topped with lettuce, tomato, pickles, and cajun sauce with a kick. You’ll surely savor the Orlando Cubano- bold roasted pulled pork and ham topped with melted provolone, pickles, mustard, and mayo. Your mind will be blown by The Joey- signature patty on a garlic pretzel bun topped with pepperoni, melted mozzarella, & marinara sauce. These are only a few of the items you’ll find on their gourmet menu. So, foodies of Decatur, we definitely think that you should check out Pinkz now AND later.
name: Pinkz
